---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-secondary-dark text-secondary-light py-12 px-6 mb-40">
    <div class="max-w-screen-lg mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-comp text-primary mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl">Effective Date: January 1, 2025</p>
      </header>

      <!-- Content -->
      <section class="space-y-8 text-sm md:text-base">
        <p>
          At <strong>Poolable LLC</strong>, we value your privacy and are committed to maintaining the trust and confidence of our visitors. This Privacy Policy outlines the information we collect, how we use it, and the choices you have regarding your personal data.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-retro text-primary">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          We collect minimal information to improve your experience and ensure the functionality of our website. Specifically, we may collect the following types of data:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside pl-4 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Non-Personal Information:</strong> Aggregated data such as website traffic statistics and general usage patterns through Google Analytics.</li>
          <li><strong>Voluntarily Provided Information:</strong> If you choose to contact us via forms or email, we may store the information you provide, such as your name and email address.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-retro text-primary">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>The information we collect is used solely for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside pl-4 space-y-2">
          <li>To analyze website performance and improve our content and services using Google Analytics.</li>
          <li>To respond to your inquiries or feedback when you contact us.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We do <strong>not</strong> use your information for retargeting, advertising, or sharing with third parties.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-retro text-primary">3. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
        <p>
          Poolable LLC uses cookies solely for basic website functionality and to gather anonymous analytics data through Google Analytics. Cookies are small text files stored on your device that help us understand website usage patterns.
        </p>
        <p>
          You can manage or delete cookies through your browser settings. For more information on Google Analytics' data practices, please visit <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" class="text-primary hover:underline">Google Analytics Privacy Overview</a>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-retro text-primary">4. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We take data security seriously and implement industry-standard measures to protect the data we collect. However, please note that no transmission of data over the internet can be guaranteed to be 100% secure.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-retro text-primary">5. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          You have the right to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside pl-4 space-y-2">
          <li>Access the personal data we may have collected about you.</li>
          <li>Request corrections or deletion of your data.</li>
          <li>Opt out of Google Analytics tracking by using tools such as <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" class="text-primary hover:underline">Googleâ€™s Opt-Out Browser Add-On</a>.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-retro text-primary">6. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>
          Our website may contain links to third-party websites. Poolable LLC is not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these external sites. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of any third-party websites you visit.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-retro text-primary">7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy as needed to reflect changes in our practices or applicable regulations. Any updates will be posted on this page with a new effective date.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-retro text-primary">8. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or how your data is handled, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Poolable LLC</strong><br>
          Email: <a href="mailto:contact@poolable.xyz" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@poolable.xyz</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
